---
const title = 'Halaman tidak ditemukan — Sinar Farma';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="id" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
    <title>{title}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main
      style="min-height:100dvh;display:grid;place-items:center;padding:32px;font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;background:#f8faf7;color:#18221a;"
    >
      <section style="max-width:640px;text-align:center;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#526256;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;">Sinar Farma</p>
        <h1 style="margin:0;color:#1d6b3a;font-size:clamp(64px,16vw,112px);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.03em;">
          404
        </h1>
        <p style="margin:24px 0 0;font-size:clamp(24px,5vw,34px);line-height:1.18;font-weight:700;">
          Halaman ini tidak tersedia.
        </p>
        <p style="margin:16px auto 0;max-width:560px;color:#526256;font-size:18px;line-height:1.65;">
          Tautan yang Anda buka mungkin sudah berubah. Kembali ke beranda untuk melihat informasi umum Sinar Farma.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/"
          style="display:inline-flex;margin-top:32px;min-height:44px;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-radius:999px;background:#1d6b3a;padding:0 22px;color:white;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;"
          >Kembali ke beranda</a
        >
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
